{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/settimeout-vs-setinterval/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"thumbzzero's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"daa6f199-c3ca-5a2d-991c-c5b96bb3cc86","excerpt":"JavaScript의 타이머 함수에는 과 가 있다. setTimeout 일정 시간 후에 한 번 실행한다. setInterval 일정 시간마다 반복 실행한다. 타이머 정리 두 함수 모두 반환된 ID로 취소할 수 있다. React에서는 두 함수 사용 시 cleanup…","html":"<p>JavaScript의 타이머 함수에는 <code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">setTimeout</code>가 있다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/setTimeout\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">setTimeout</a></h2>\n<p><strong>일정 시간 후에 한 번</strong> 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'1초 후 실행'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/setInterval\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">setInterval</a></h2>\n<p><strong>일정 시간마다 반복</strong> 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'1초마다 실행'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>타이머 정리</h2>\n<p>두 함수 모두 반환된 ID로 취소할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> timeoutId <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">clearTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>timeoutId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> intervalId <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">clearInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>intervalId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>React에서는 두 함수 사용 시 cleanup 함수에서 정리를 해주어야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">doSomething</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">clearInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>비동기 작업과 함께 쓸 때</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code>은 <strong>내부 비동기 작업의 완료 여부와 관계없이</strong> 일정 간격으로 콜백을 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/api/data'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 이 요청이 1초 넘게 걸린다면?</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code>은 콜백을 실행시킬 뿐, 그 안의 비동기 작업이 끝나는지 신경 쓰지 않는다. 이전 <code class=\"language-text\">fetch</code>가 아직 응답을 기다리는 중이어도 1초 후엔 다음 콜백을 실행하기 때문에, <strong>요청이 동시에 여러 개 쌓일 수 있다.</strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">setTimeout</code>을 재귀로 쓰면 <strong>이전 작업이 끝난 후</strong> 다음 타이머가 시작된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">repeat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/api/data'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 작업이 끝난 후</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1초 후에 다음 실행</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>작업이 3초 걸리면 그게 끝난 뒤 1초 후에 다음 요청을 보내므로 요청이 겹칠 일이 없다.</p>\n<p>[참고] <a href=\"/polling\">폴링(Polling)</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>실제로 어떻게 차이나는지</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">setInterval (간격 1초, 작업 3초)\n|---작업A(3초)---|\n    |---작업B(3초)---|  ← 1초 후 시작, A와 겹침\n        |---작업C(3초)---|  ← 또 겹침\n\n재귀 setTimeout (간격 1초, 작업 3초)\n|---작업A(3초)---|--1초--|---작업B(3초)---|--1초--|---작업C(3초)---|\n                         ↑ A 끝난 후 1초 후에 시작</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>정확한 딜레이가 보장되지 않는다</h2>\n<p>두 함수 모두 딜레이가 <strong>정확히</strong> 보장되지 않는다는 걸 알아두면 좋다.</p>\n<p>타이머 콜백은 태스크 큐에 들어간다. 콜스택이 바쁘면 지정한 시간이 지나도 바로 실행되지 않을 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'1초 후?'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 콜스택이 바쁘면 1초보다 늦게 실행될 수 있다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 무거운 작업</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2>정리</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">setTimeout</code>은 한 번, <code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code>은 반복 실행이다</li>\n<li>React에서는 cleanup 함수에서 타이머를 정리해야 한다</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code>은 내부 비동기 작업의 완료 여부와 관계없이 실행되어 네트워크 요청이 겹칠 수 있다</li>\n<li>비동기 작업을 반복할 때는 재귀 <code class=\"language-text\">setTimeout</code>이 안전하다</li>\n<li>두 함수 모두 딜레이가 정확히 보장되지 않는다. 콜스택이 바쁘면 늦게 실행될 수 있다</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"setTimeout vs setInterval","date":"May 30, 2026","description":"setTimeout과 setInterval의 차이, 비동기 작업에서 올바르게 사용하는 법","tags":["JavaScript"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/reflow-repaint/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Reflow와 Repaint"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/polling/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"폴링(Polling)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"daa6f199-c3ca-5a2d-991c-c5b96bb3cc86","previousPostId":"568c3aeb-c2dc-569f-b2c4-a0789a07f79a","nextPostId":"7404b00d-dc3c-5bf9-bc85-6e1afb4a2a3e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}